        },
        {
          "commText": "B0$ Royal Challengers Bengaluru come into this match at a tricky time. After recent losses to GT and LSG, they have dropped to 4th place on the points table. While they are still in the hunt for the playoffs, their lead is shrinking. Team missed Phil Salt due to a finger injury (who is reportedly fit for today's game) and fast bowler Josh Hazlewood has struggled lately, giving away too many runs. Playing in Raipur adds another challenge because RCB could practice only for an hour at the venue due to rain. They need to win today to stay in the top four and stop their recent slide.",
